[[Venthan Chassu/Legends|Venthan Chassu's]] '''Selonian nude studies''' was an artwork of [[Selonian/Legends|Selonian]] observations said to capture both their form and their privacy.

The piece of fine art was on public display at the [[Museum of Fine Art|Coronet City Museum of Fine Art]] on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]] before being limited to rare private showings.

